Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.20,0:00:04.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在海浪声中一边欣赏 一边不断地眺望着海面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.49,0:00:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会忘却时光的流逝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.15,0:00:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人啊还是忙一点好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.67,0:00:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 忙过头了也会忘记时间的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.11,0:00:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过犹不及 太过忙碌或空闲 都会忘记时间的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.77,0:00:16.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.21,0:00:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.93,0:00:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 发呆的时间结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.92,0:00:25.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱 今天是亚利亚公司的创立纪念日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 就是祖母创立亚利亚公司的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.77,0:00:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天全天休业
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.60,0:00:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和艾莉西亚前辈 亚利亚社长三人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.65,0:00:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去进行我们一直期待的短途旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.64,0:00:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.29,0:02:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是自行车呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.59,0:02:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个新布拉诺岛上可以骑自行车呢 不过限制在十二岁以下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来AQUA以后 还是第一次见到自行车呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.51,0:02:32.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各式各样不同颜色风格的房子好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.45,0:02:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在地球上的布拉诺岛也和这里一样是个渔村
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.02,0:02:41.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说 以前捕鱼归来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.73,0:02:45.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了渔人在漆黑的雾霭中也能回到自己的家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.63,0:02:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渔人的妻子们想出办法 将房子涂上绚丽的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.18,0:02:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在也还保留着这种传统呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.54,0:03:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那个是地球时代的威尼斯人大厅中所展示的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.31,0:03:03.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被称作威尼斯网纹的编织品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 说起捕鱼 渔网是很重要的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.73,0:03:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结网技术发展的结果就是诞生艺术品了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.09,0:03:14.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AQUA也继承了这份技术呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.24,0:03:19.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿那件婚纱的新娘一定会十分美丽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上要拜访的安娜前辈的网纹婚纱装很惊艳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.90,0:03:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…那位安娜前辈是位什么样的人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.18,0:03:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说来 是位开朗并且引人注目的领航员呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.70,0:03:41.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,众多的男性为她着迷 比起现在的我来说更加忙碌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.01,0:03:44.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好厉害的一位前辈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:47.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不觉心跳也加速了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.60,0:03:53.55,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(433,290)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那段 缓缓流逝的时光中…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.47,0:04:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这栋房子 艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:17.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 有人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.95,0:04:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是出门了吗？应该没有弄错约定的时间呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:41.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:48.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:56.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点问题想问…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:04:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:03.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有两个女生在门口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.79,0:05:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.14,0:05:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:10.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件制服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:12.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了 艾莉西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.84,0:05:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 你就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.48,0:05:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:23.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面 我叫水无灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.98,0:05:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.11,0:05:28.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是安娜 这边的是我家的儿子亚西多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 亚西多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.42,0:05:32.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:36.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 怎么一下子就脸红啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.13,0:05:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本没有脸红！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.22,0:05:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀 一被挑拨就上当啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.34,0:05:42.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了 死老太婆！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.06,0:05:44.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.85,0:05:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.80,0:06:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这幅网纹编织真是上品啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:02.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.76,0:06:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是奶奶织的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:06.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？奶奶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.94,0:06:11.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我奶奶是这个小镇有名的网纹编织工艺人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.45,0:06:13.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈现在也在那边学习
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.24,0:06:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还是个生手就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:17.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.03,0:06:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件是结婚时收到的贺礼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.93,0:06:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的都是自己做的 但是收到的礼物也有不少
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.22,0:06:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈在亚利亚公司工作的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的丈夫 当时在这座小镇作渔夫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.07,0:06:47.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和他的母亲两人去新威尼斯观光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.96,0:06:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后 前辈和深爱母亲的渔夫就坠入了爱河
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.97,0:07:05.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十分感谢您能原谅我的任性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.46,0:07:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 安娜 恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是件可喜可贺的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你毫不犹豫地走自己的道路 这使我很高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢您 祖母
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:21.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 艾莉西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.15,0:07:25.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要注意身体哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.13,0:07:26.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.24,0:07:42.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚公司留下了我的青春
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好软好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.84,0:07:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸福的婚姻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:56.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不尽然呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.48,0:07:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.15,0:08:04.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 嫁到小岛上后也很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.05,0:08:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和在那之前的领航员生活完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.06,0:08:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熟人一个也没有 丈夫总是在外打渔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:19.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在岛上的人际关系也陷入僵局 很难融入他们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时好寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.32,0:08:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 开始编织网纹的时候 就和岛上的人们接触多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:43.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时一件网纹编织品就要分工给五个人做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.35,0:08:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.67,0:08:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里和这里 网纹的刺绣要由不同的人来做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刺绣与刺绣之间的连接和边缘上的刺绣是我的份
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得好高兴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.77,0:09:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件刺绣是将安娜前辈和岛上的人们连接起来的桥梁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.03,0:09:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 嘴真甜啊 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.09,0:09:09.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:10.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知祖母身体是否健康呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 阿尔贝特捕鱼回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.53,0:09:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.44,0:09:28.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祖母 您怎么来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚把我叫过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:34.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了 安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.68,0:09:36.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到你精神饱满的样子 我很高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.69,0:09:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才在那边突然遇上的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能见到您真的十分高兴啊 祖母
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.09,0:09:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.43,0:09:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 亚西多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.04,0:09:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.89,0:09:55.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面 我是阿尔贝特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.46,0:09:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是水无灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:09:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收获怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.67,0:10:03.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 选了些特别好吃的拿过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.05,0:10:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去很好吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.78,0:10:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那么 我也得拿出点本事才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.02,0:10:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.02,0:10:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烤得正好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.51,0:10:21.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.25,0:10:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.09,0:10:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:35.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔贝特 吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:37.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 马上过去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.31,0:10:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真丰盛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.31,0:10:45.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 别客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:47.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开动了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.70,0:10:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鱼很新鲜 真美味
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您过奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:02.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 祖母 请喝点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.20,0:11:04.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.12,0:11:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.83,0:11:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.65,0:11:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手艺真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.02,0:11:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家看上去好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.71,0:11:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上也是很早出门的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是人来疯过头而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.35,0:12:09.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有许多我所不知道的亚利亚公司的历史呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.94,0:12:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从亚利亚公司创立伊始的旧人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到最年轻的新进成员 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.11,0:12:18.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家聚在一起 总觉得很高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.95,0:12:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚西多也像自己的孙子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 在这里 发生了名为「这样聚在一起」的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.82,0:12:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:38.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇迹…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都是多亏祖母创立了亚利亚公司的缘故
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.43,0:12:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不是这样的话 我和阿尔贝特相遇的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.89,0:12:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 还有生下亚西多的事情都不会发生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.44,0:13:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安娜 你扎扎实实地走自己的道路 珍惜每天的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.86,0:13:11.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算是找到属于自己的幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:16.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.93,0:13:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚公司并非由我一人之力而建成的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:28.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是亚利亚社长让我注意到了这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 应该说是救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.10,0:13:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚社长它？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.78,0:13:38.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果方便的话 能说给我们听听吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:44.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候 我就快迷失自我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:51.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我还在姬屋当领航员的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.66,0:13:57.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作辛苦了 秋乃前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:14:00.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作辛苦了 秋乃前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.87,0:14:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时 我还人称姬屋的王牌 整整14年过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 秋乃前辈 今天仍然亮丽迷人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:14.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅仅只是从身边走过 气氛就为之一变
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.98,0:14:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说 昨天她就「摆平」了6组指名她的客人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:22.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害 要是我的话绝对累到趴下了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:28.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然都说岁月不饶人 但是她反而越来越闪耀动人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.44,0:14:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么忙碌 也不会露出不耐烦的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直就是当代第一的水精灵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.44,0:15:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.35,0:15:01.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 玩得真尽兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.56,0:15:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.87,0:15:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:42.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 小猫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.59,0:15:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近 你总是待在这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.81,0:15:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是从哪里来的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:51.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天在这里干些什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.17,0:15:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说 迷路了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直待在同一个地方 不感到厌倦吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 突然问了那么多问题 你会很困扰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:17:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那段时间里我虽然也很热爱工作 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.08,0:17:06.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为过于繁忙 周围的时间流逝得也很快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.91,0:17:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候不禁会觉得有点可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:16.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这个世界上还有着很多美妙的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.91,0:17:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真希望每一件事物都能用心地慢慢培养下去 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.09,0:17:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 小猫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.37,0:17:32.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总在这里凝视着什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.67,0:17:41.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在等待着什么重要的东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.07,0:18:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小猫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.82,0:18:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样执着 到底在等什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:54.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小猫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.34,0:19:14.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回过神来的时候 已经是早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.70,0:19:18.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明淋了一整晚的雨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.53,0:19:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是感到神清气爽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才察觉到了我一直在勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.28,0:19:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是 我和亚利亚社长 开创了亚利亚公司
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.78,0:19:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想一起看看 它那美丽的蓝色眼睛中显现的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.53,0:20:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（油漆未干 请注意）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.31,0:20:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,故事就是这样开场的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.67,0:21:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.81,0:21:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.31,0:21:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将来总有一天 灯里会开始经营亚利亚公司
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.87,0:21:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正期待着还不为人所知的属于灯里的亚利亚公司
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.78,0:21:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.88,0:21:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.53,0:22:08.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱 我加入亚利亚公司 真是非常幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.70,0:22:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我和这么温柔有情的人们在一起过着每一天的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.87,0:22:20.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里姐姐 亚利亚公司的美好之处
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.58,0:22:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能在于很多人的感情和愿望中揉合了温柔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.12,0:22:28.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真羡慕你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.28,0:24:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 灯里前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.59,0:24:09.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超 超级SOS
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.25,0:24:10.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 怎么啦？爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.81,0:24:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前辈 SOS
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.50,0:24:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.38,0:24:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那份 珍重之人的记忆…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.20,0:24:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 请握住我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPJP】
